name: Keen Labs, Inc.
description: Developer of a backend analytics infrastructure designed to help developers in every industry leverage data in new and inventive ways. The company's platform can capture event data and embed custom dashboards in any application, giving developers the flexibility and extensibility of a custom analytics stack, without the hassle and risk of managing big data infrastructure.
